[div class=p 
	"RNG changes every frame 
	$LF
	"Using different inputs beforehand results can change. Sometimes waiting for more favorable outcomes is better.
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=ItemManipulation 
	" Item manipulation
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Enemy item drops also change every frame.
	$LF
	"Item drops can be changed slightly by waiting for the right frame like before, which can only be done without leveling up afterwards.
	$LF
	"Or alternately, after leveling up there are 7 frames in which varying inputs change the outcome of the drop. Or using both these methods at the same time.
	$LF
	"However there's no guarantee getting the items you want while doing this. So it's just trial and error until you get the item drop you want.
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=HolyWater 
	" Holy water
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Holy water is obtained by handing in red snappers to Korin. It temporarily gives 25 points to all stats when used.
	$LF
]div
