[h3 id=SwitchSkip 
	" Switch skip
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Saving and restart to reset blood cell rng, getting a single blood cell past the door using ki blasts and using instant transmission once it's in the right position in order to get through the door.
	$LF
	"It skips having to through multiple loading zones, breaking three switches, watching a cut scene and backtracking.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Gotenks and Piccolo fights can be skipped through gaps in an invisible wall.
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=CandyClip 
	" Candy clip
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"You can skip the last fight inside Buu by having Buu turn Goku into candy and standing near the door in the correct position while buu eats him.
	$LF
	"This puts Goku right into the loading zone, triggering the next cut scene.
	$LF
]div
