	(__wikiLink|displaytext=last submission|href=/6239S)
	" because they chose to stop input before the credits instead of getting back to the main menu. The basic movement optimization is pretty much on point. It also appears that a lot of thought was put into distributing experience between characters so that the level gates are opened with as little grinding as possible. I appreciated the sequences of rapid-fire equipment drops thanks to some quality RNG manipulation. There aren't too many skips, but the ones you found are quite effective.
	$LF
